files.name: .editorconfig
files.content:
root = true

# Unix-style newlines with a newline ending every file
[*]
end_of_line = lf
insert_final_newline = true
charset = utf-8

[*.{html,js,ts,css,scss,xml}]
indent_style = space
indent_size = 4
trim_trailing_whitespace = true

[*.yml]
indent_style = space
indent_size = 2
